Oregon Big Game Regulations provided by Oregon Department of Fish and Wildlife http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/hunting/big_game/regulations/

srcinfo.srccontr: Oregon Big Game Regulations textual descriptions; BLM Ground Transportation (public) geodatabase; 2004 ODF Public Land Ownership data; Streamnet Pacific Northwest Hydrography Framework; OR BLM Hydrologic units data

procstep.procdesc: Traced lines for each unit from the following data layers: BLM Ground Transportation (public) geodatabase, 2004 ODF Public Land Ownership data, Streamnet Pacific Northwest Hydrography Framework, OR BLM Hydrologic units, to reflect the boundary descriptions provided in the Oregon Big Game Regulation textual descriptions.
Attributed unit polygons with unit number and unit name.
Imported layer into geodatabase and added layer to a topology with rules set as follows: must contain no gaps, must not overlap.
Cleaned up the line data to reflect topology rules. Fixed polygon errors.

Made corrections to the following unit boundaries: Beatys Butte/Juniper, Pine Creek/Keating, Catherine Creek/Minam/Keating, Evans Creek/Applegate, Warm Springs/White River, Desolation/Sumpter, Wilson/Saddle Mountain, Trask.
Proofed all unit boundaries and updated metadata
Updated Minam/Catherine Creek boundary to reflect new 2008 big game regulation changes.
Updated Catherine Creek/Keating boundary to reflect new 2010 big game regulation changes.
